                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Chlothar's illegitimate son who became a hilichurl and fell into a coma after the Cataclysm. Chlothar used an Abyssal power to cure his son and wanted him to become the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 5747,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/09/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_1714599439243588643.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Loom of Fate",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Vedrfolnir",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"The Visionary,\" one of the five Sinners of Khaenri'ah, a transcendent being who answered Chlothar's prayers and helped his son. Chlothar swore to honor the \"god\" that has honored his wishes.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Under Vedrfolnir's influence, Alberich established the Abyss Order.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Abyss Order",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "An organization established by Chlothar Alberich. Its main goal is to destroy the nations watched over by The Seven because of the destruction of Khaenri'ah by the gods.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Sibling",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Traveler's sibling who became the Princess/Prince of the Abyss Order.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
